Description: Genesis meta-package for Distiller CM5 platform
 This meta-package installs all required components for the Distiller CM5
 platform, including hardware drivers, system services, and management tools.
 .
 This package ensures a complete and consistent installation of the Distiller
 software stack on the CM5 hardware platform.
